#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Although it does not happen often, sometimes a new currency is "
#| "introduced. This can be a new virtual currency, such as Bitcoin, or a "
#| "change introduced by a country for financial policy reasons. While any "
#| "such currency will be added to the next version of &kappname; it is "
#| "possible to add it manually, in case you have a need to begin using it "
#| "immediately."
msgid ""
"Although it does not happen often, sometimes a new currency is introduced. "
"This can be a new virtual currency, such as Bitcoin, or a change introduced "
"by a country for financial policy reasons. While any such currency will be "
"added to the next version of &kmymoney;, it is possible to add it to your "
"data file manually, in case you have a need to begin using it immediately."
msgstr ""
"Kuigi seda ei juhtu sageli, ilmub mõnikord ometi uusi vääringuid. Need "
"võivad olla uued virtuaalvääringud, näiteks Bitcoin, või siis muudab mõni "
"riik finantspoliitilistel põhjustel oma rahaühikut. Selline vääring "
"lisatakse kindlasti &kappname; uude versiooni,. aga kui sul peaks seda "
"kiiremini vaja olema, saab selle lisada ka käsitsi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To manually add a currency, bring up the Currencies dialog, as shown above. "
"Right-click any existing currency and select <guimenuitem>New currency</"
"guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Currency Options</guimenu> context menu, or "
"click <guibutton>New</guibutton>. This will bring up the <guilabel>Currency "
"editor</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

