#. Tag: title
#: details-currencies.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering transactions using different currencies"
msgstr "Tehingute sisestamine muid vääringuid kasutades"

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:174
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Whenever a transaction is entered that refers to more than one currency, "
#| "the exchange rate editor pops up and allows you to enter an exchange "
#| "rate. Initially, the current price available from the price database will "
#| "be used as exchange rate. See <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
#| "\">Entering exchange rates for currencies</link> for more information on "
#| "how to provide exchange rates manually and obtain online price "
#| "information."
msgid ""
"Whenever a transaction is entered that refers to more than one currency, the "
"exchange rate editor pops up and allows you to enter an exchange rate. "
"Initially, the most recent price available from the price database will be "
"used as the exchange rate. See <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
"\">Entering exchange rates for currencies</link> for more information on how "
"to provide exchange rates manually and obtain online price information."
msgstr ""
"Kui sisestatakse tehing, mis viitab mitmele vääringule, ilmub vahetuskursi "
"redaktor, kus saab sisestada vahetuskursi. Algselt kasutatakse "
"vahetuskursina aktiivset hinda, mida pakub hindade andmebaas. Täpsemalt "
"kõneleb sellest, kuidas määrata vääringukursid käsitsi ja hankida "
"internetist hinnateavet, osa <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
"\">Vääringute vahetuskursi sisestamine</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally, the exchange rate is saved in the price database once entered by "
"the user."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks salvestatakse vahetuskurss otsekohe pärast kasutaja sisestust hindade "
"andmebaasi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-currencies.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exchange rates for currencies"
msgstr "Vääringute vahetuskursid"

#. Tag: title
#: details-currencies.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering prices manually"
msgstr "Hindade sisestamine käsitsi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The price database editor allows you to enter exchange rates between "
#| "currencies or prices for investments. You can pull it up using the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prices...</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice> menu option."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Price Editor</guilabel>, also called the price database "
"editor, allows you to enter or modify prices for both investments and "
"exchange rates between currencies. You can pull it up using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prices...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Hindade redaktor võimaldab sisestada vääringute vahetuskursid või "
"investeeringute hinnad. Selle saab avada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu><guimenuitem>Hinnad...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
