#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:239
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you press the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button, you get the New "
#| "Price Entry dialog. Enter the first currency (USD in the example above) "
#| "in the Security field. Enter the second currency (EUR in the example "
#| "above) in the Currency field. Enter the effective date of the price in "
#| "the Date field."
msgid ""
"Enter the first currency (USD in the example above) in the Security field. "
"Enter the second currency (EUR in the example above) in the Currency field. "
"Enter the effective date of the price in the Date field."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga nupule <guibutton>Uus</guibutton> ilmub uue hinna sisestamise "
"dialoog. Sisesta väljale Väärtpaber esimene vääring (ülaltoodud näites USD). "
"Sisesta väljale Vääring teine vääring (ülaltoodud näites EUR). Sisesta hinna "
"kehtivuspäev väljale Kuupäev."

#. Tag: para
#: details-currencies.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
